          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Right to Lend Act of 2017</b></p> <p>This bill repeals provisions of the Equal Credit Opportunity Act that require a financial institution, in the case of an application for credit by a business, to&nbsp;request information regarding whether the business is a women-owned, minority-owned, or small business.</p>]]></text>
